720
00:42:11.532 --> 00:42:15.472
But where we've been, to sort of summarize, looking at it as an immunologist

721
00:42:16.332 --> 00:42:20.052
and looking at oncology, was that it always used to be just

722
00:42:20.092 --> 00:42:23.472
