723
00:42:24.492 --> 00:42:28.432
a significant fraction of those lived longer, and this is

724
00:42:28.492 --> 00:42:32.462
with really bad diseases, longer than the controls, and calling

725
00:42:32.512 --> 00:42:36.472
that a victory. We know that ipilimumab and PD-1 can both do that.

726
00:42:36.572 --> 00:42:40.352
