736
00:43:11.320 --> 00:43:14.780
a little bit more planned way, or where we take a look at the

737
00:43:15.000 --> 00:43:18.300
microenvironment first, and maybe and then decide what to do.

738
00:43:18.360 --> 00:43:20.580
We could structure these sorts of attacks much better.

739
00:43:21.000 --> 00:43:24.720
But I think our goal should be to cure as many patients as

740
00:43:24.760 --> 00:43:27.680
